data.description: Fantastically Upgraded and Turnkey Four Seasons Murrieta 55+ Active Retirement Community home! RARE FIND 3 CAR GARAGE! This Provincial 1 Floor Plan featuring 2,262 sq ft located on a nearly 12k foot lot with a PAID FOR 22 PANEL SOLAR SYSTEM. This home is just loaded with upgrades! As you enter the home past the glass front door, you will see the custom tile floor, baseboard and crown molding throughout, in addition to the custom light fixtures and plantation shutters. The kitchen has granite counters, maple cabinets, updated appliances including double ovens, 5 burner range, built in fridge, a butler's pantry, and lots of storage! The stone facade bar opens to the family room with gas fireplace and shutters. There are LED lights throughout the home with dimmer switches. The "beach designed" primary bedroom has a retreat with a fireplace, wood flooring, custom wall coverings and fans, walk-in closet, granite counters with dual sinks, a walk-in shower with glass tile surround, and separate tub. Guest bedroom with ceiling fan and wood floors. Third bedroom is perfect for an office or art studio! Guest bathroom has dual sinks. Separate laundry room with deep sink. 3 car garage with custom lighting, insulated garage doors. The back yard is perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing in the afternoons and evenings, with a solid Alumawood patio cover with 2 ceiling fans and lights, custom landscape with 38 drains and a fenced garden. This home is turnkey, highly upgraded, and a must-see for any buyer looking in Four Seasons Murrieta! Don't miss the Lodge. The Club House is a 10 acre facility for the use of Four Seasons residents and their guests only, and includes a ballroom, gym, conference room, library, beauty salon, card and game rooms, heated pool, bocce ball court, paddle tennis and tennis courts, shuffleboard, horseshoes and more...
